yTime":"2017-09-02T16:41:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 靚腳有冇your face your fate咖？例如一對中上腳，生係靚女上就容易被歸納為靚腳，生係醜女上就只可以成為普通腳⋯⋯"},{"pid":"9dc45db937311fff0dbfea9bbfedb9ec9a786e59","tid":384760,"uid":126490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T16:52:59.000Z","msg":"我身長腳短<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 本身唔肥但因為腳粗搞到睇落肥 好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e63c54e30bdf5b66cdc5007abf8360f452898dde","tid":384760,"uid":62837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T16:56:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實肌肉邊有咁易練到粗，通常係皮下脂肪厚。<br />\n如果你真係肌肉粗，你去做負重，然後多菜少肉少飯，好快冇哂啲肌肉。<br />\n不過九成九係脂肪</blockquote><br />\n因為少運動又冇乜肌肉又長時間企係度,令到血液同淋巴液循環力降低<br />\n女人比較多,通常係下半身屎忽到小腿會腫<br />\n建議按摩下對腳,練下半身肌肉"},{"pid":"39c6b495c3a5b2ab0bf46b9270760ee373fe52c4","tid":384760,"uid":143136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T16:56:34.000Z","msg":"仆開有條街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成隻腳都係"},{"pid":"7107fc13c012b54ae49552bf687f33a6661a5f3c","tid":384760,"uid":143136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T16:56:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>仆開有條路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成隻腳都係</blockquote>"},{"pid":"b53dbf0d762996b4b855d8c8867e4de1146aaf91","tid":384760,"uid":134105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T17:07:14.000Z","msg":"打波成日仆到膝頭哥傷哂，有好多疤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cfab6f4ae0d4ad7442ab640083c5252d543076f","tid":384760,"uid":6883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T17:26:56.000Z","msg":"無都大把仔要啦"},{"pid":"eff627ba3d9f5ca0d900510012aa6d6360f339e7","tid":384760,"uid":76451,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T17:34:14.000Z","msg":"一樣都係冇靚腳 中學好鐘意踢波 小腿好壯<br />\n係咁啱識既男朋